title: HTML5_ The Missing Manual.epub
description: HTML5 is more than a markup languageit's a dozen independent web standards all rolled into one. Until now, all its been missing is a manual. With this thorough, jargon-free guide, you'll learn how to build web apps that include video tools, dynamic drawings, geolocation, offline web apps, drag-and-drop, and many other features. HTML5 is the future of the Web, and with this book you'll reach it quickly.
